name: Ms. Dara
description:
Ibu Dara is a main chatacter from an iconic 2009 Indonesian horror classic ‘Rumah Dara’. i chose kak @ianhugen to be part of this illustration since she’s one of my favorite person alive, and my favorite speaker that ever featured on one of Menjadi Manusia’s segments. i love her stories, her works, and her impact to the society, i hope she will always be this generous to share her stories to the millions of Indonesian.

a part of my Inktober serial Illustrations titled ‘Indonesian Horror Stories’. 

thank you!
